  "title": "Accounts Cum Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accounts cum Admin Executive </strong></p><ul><li>Assist in preparing monthly Accounts and finance-related reports.</li><li>Assist in coordinating meetings and handling correspondence with relevant authorities.</li><li>Assist in planning, coordinating, and executing fundraising events and activities</li><li>Assist in updating and adhering to organisational policies and charitable regulatory requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or degree in Accountancy, Finance or relevant field.</li><li>Strong communication and excellent writing skills.</li><li>Ability to translate documents between English and Chinese.</li><li>A minimum of three years of relevant experience within a non-profit or charitable organisaiton is preferred. </li></ul><p>To apply for the position, please submit your CV along with your salary expectations. Please note that incomplete submissions will be rejected. Only candidates who are shortlisted will be contacted for interview arrangements.</p>",
